title: Population by Districts, Afghanistan (March 21, 2002 -- March 20, 2003)
name: Population by Districts, Afghanistan (March 21, 2002 -- March 20, 2003)
description:
This is a district level shapefile of Afghanistan that shows the total population, total population of rural and urban males and females for the time period March 21, 2002-March 20, 2003. The data comes from the 2003 Afghanistan Statistical Yearbook. 

Data was uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
